s_report/ngs_rep.html">A Forest That Refuses to Disappear: Cycles        of Environmental Degeneration and Regeneration in Jordan </a>(Report to        the National Geographic Society Research Grant Number 5758-96) </span></td>   </tr></tbody></table><hr size="5" /> <span style="color: #af0000; font-family: Book Antiqua,Times New Roman,Times; font-size: xx-small;"><b><span style="color: #af0000; font-family: Book Antiqua,Times New Roman,Times;"><b><span style="color: #660033;">LaBianca</span></b></span>,    <span style="color: #660033;">Oystein S. ,</span></b></span><span style="color: #660033; font-size: xx-small;"><b><span style="font-family: Book Antiqua,Times New Roman,Times;">    Larry G. Herr, Randall W. Younker, Lawrence T. Geraty, Douglas R. Clark</span></b></span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><br /></span> <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr>      <td valign="BASELINE" width="42"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><img align="BOTTOM" height="15" hspace="13" src="http://www.casa.arizona.edu/_themes/expeditn/expbul1a.gif" width="15" /></span> </td>     <td valign="TOP" width="100%"><span style="font-family: Book Antiqua,Times New Roman,Times; font-size: xx-small;"><a href="http://www.casa.arizona.edu/MPP/mpp_96/96_mpp_report.html">Report on the 1996 Field Season of the Madaba        Plains Project</a></span></td>   </tr></tbody></table><span style="font-family: Book Antiqua,Times New Roman,Times; font-size: xx-small;"> </span> <hr size="5" /> <span style="color: #660033; font-family: Book Antiqua,Times New Roman,Times; font-size: xx-small;"><b>Ray    Jr., Paul J. &amp; Oystein S. LaBianca</b></span><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><br /></span> <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr>      <td valign="BASELINE" width="42"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><img align="BOTTOM" height="15" hspace="13" src="http://www.casa.arizona.edu/_themes/expeditn/expbul1a.gif" width="15" /></span> </td>     <td valign="TO